---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Studio — Full-service enrollment marketing for Higher Education" description="701am Studio — full-service enrollment marketing for universities, edtech, and agencies. Strategy, creative, lead generation, earned media, rankings, and AI visibility — scoped, staffed, and managed on your behalf.">
<!-- HERO -->
<header class="ind-hero" id="top">
  <div class="hero-atmos"><div class="grid"></div><div class="glow g1"></div><div class="glow g2"></div><div class="glow g3"></div></div>
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="ind-eyebrow"><a class="bk" href="/">701am</a> / Studio</div>
    <h1>The enrollment marketing agency built for <em class="grad">this decade</em>.</h1>
    <p class="isub">Not a PR firm. Not a software demo. A full-service enrollment marketing agency for higher education — strategy, creative, lead generation through owned and third-party networks, earned media, rankings, and AI visibility. <b>Scoped, staffed, and managed on your behalf.</b></p>
    <div class="hero-ctas">
      <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg btn-studio"><i class="ti ti-sparkles"></i>Inquire about Studio</a>
      <a href="#services" class="btn btn-soft btn-lg"><i class="ti ti-arrow-down"></i>See our services</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</header>

<!-- TRUST STRIP -->
<section class="band wrap" style="padding-top:0;padding-bottom:14px">
  <div class="studio-note" style="max-width:100%;text-align:center;justify-content:center">
    <i class="ti ti-shield-check"></i>
    <div>
      <strong>Independence guarantee.</strong> Our rankings, data, and editorial are independently maintained and never for sale. Studio services are operationally separate from our editorial work, and sponsored material is always labeled. Same sourced, no-invented-numbers standard across everything we produce.
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- SERVICES -->
<section class="band wrap" id="services">
  <div class="sec-head">
    <div class="sec-eyebrow">Our services</div>
    <h2>Full-funnel enrollment marketing, <em class="grad">end to end</em>.</h2>
    <p>From market research and creative through lead generation, earned media, rankings, and AI visibility — every service scoped to your institutional goals.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="studio-cards">
    <div class="scard">
      <span class="sc-tag" style="background:var(--coral-soft);color:var(--coral-deep)">Strategy</span>
      <h3>Enrollment Marketing</h3>
      <p>Full-funnel enrollment marketing campaigns — from audience research and creative development through multi-channel execution. We build the strategic marketing guide, position your programs, and manage integrated campaigns that connect awareness to application.</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Market research &amp; audience discovery</li>
        <li>Strategic marketing guide &amp; program positioning</li>
        <li>Creative development &amp; content production</li>
        <li>Multi-channel campaign management &amp; optimization</li>
      </ul>
      <div class="sc-foot">
        <div class="sc-best">Best for <b>universities launching or growing programs</b></div>
        <div class="sc-price">Retainers from $5,000/mo</div>
        <a href="/contact" class="sc-cta">Start a conversation <i class="ti ti-arrow-right"></i></a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="scard">
      <span class="sc-tag" style="background:var(--amber-soft);color:var(--amber-deep)">Leads</span>
      <h3>Lead Generation &amp; Performance Marketing</h3>
      <p>Quality inquiry generation at scale — through our in-house network of owned education properties and a managed third-party publisher marketplace. Audience targeting, paid media, and organic placements that deliver high-intent prospective students at efficient cost-per-lead.</p>
      <ul>
        <li>In-house network placements (owned properties)</li>
        <li>Third-party publisher network management</li>
        <li>Paid search, social &amp; display campaign management</li>
        <li>Audience targeting &amp; segmentation</li>
      </ul>
      <div class="sc-foot">
        <div class="sc-best">Best for <b>programs needing inquiry volume at scale</b></div>
        <div class="sc-price">Performance-based or retainer</div>
        <a href="/contact" class="sc-cta">Start a conversation <i class="ti ti-arrow-right"></i></a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="scard">
      <span class="sc-tag" style="background:var(--slate-soft);color:var(--slate-blue)">Media</span>
      <h3>Earned Media &amp; AI Visibility</h3>
      <p>Full-cycle earned media for enrollment — data-story research through journalist outreach, placement tracking, and funnel correlation. Every placement feeds AI citations, search rankings, and press mentions simultaneously.</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Data-story research &amp; narrative development</li>
        <li>Journalist outreach &amp; reporter relationship management</li>
        <li>AI citation strategy &amp; optimization</li>
        <li>Funnel correlation from placement to inquiry</li>
      </ul>
      <div class="sc-foot">
        <div class="sc-best">Best for <b>enrollment teams, category leaders</b></div>
        <div class="sc-price">Retainers from $3,500/mo</div>
        <a href="/contact" class="sc-cta">Start a conversation <i class="ti ti-arrow-right"></i></a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="scard">
      <span class="sc-tag" style="background:var(--indigo-soft);color:var(--indigo-deep)">Authority</span>
      <h3>Rankings &amp; Data Visibility</h3>
      <p>Earn the rankings, outcomes data, and third-party coverage that build category authority and make your institution the default answer when AI, journalists, and prospective students evaluate your programs.</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Program &amp; school rankings strategy</li>
        <li>Outcomes data publishing &amp; distribution</li>
        <li>Third-party directory &amp; review placement</li>
        <li>Competitor displacement through data superiority</li>
      </ul>
      <div class="sc-foot">
        <div class="sc-best">Best for <b>universities, OPMs, systems</b></div>
        <div class="sc-price">Custom, scoped to program count</div>
        <a href="/contact" class="sc-cta">Start a conversation <i class="ti ti-arrow-right"></i></a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="scard">
      <span class="sc-tag" style="background:var(--green-soft);color:var(--green-deep)">Narrative</span>
      <h3>Content &amp; Thought Leadership</h3>
      <p>Position your leadership and your institution's story in the publications, podcasts, and platforms that your audience already trusts — with the data and rigor that makes coverage stick and feeds enrollment.</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Executive thought leadership &amp; bylines</li>
        <li>Podcast, keynote &amp; panel placement</li>
        <li>Co-published research &amp; whitepapers</li>
        <li>Newsletter and homepage features</li>
      </ul>
      <div class="sc-foot">
        <div class="sc-best">Best for <b>university leadership, agencies</b></div>
        <div class="sc-price">From $2,000/mo</div>
        <a href="/contact" class="sc-cta">Start a conversation <i class="ti ti-arrow-right"></i></a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="scard scard-plus">
      <div class="scard-plus-inner">
        <i class="ti ti-layers-intersect"></i>
        <h3>All of it, together</h3>
        <p>Most of our clients combine multiple services — enrollment marketing feeds the brand, lead generation fills the funnel, earned media builds credibility, and rankings close the decision. We scope the full stack and run it as a single program.</p>
        <a href="/contact" class="sc-cta">Tell us what you need <i class="ti ti-arrow-right"></i></a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- HOW IT WORKS -->
<section class="studio-process">
  <div class="atmos"><div class="dg dg1"></div></div>
  <div class="wrap inner">
    <div class="sec-head">
      <div class="sec-eyebrow" style="color:#E89B7E">Our process</div>
      <h2 style="color:#fff">From discovery to enrollment. <em class="grad">A proven methodology.</em></h2>
      <p style="color:var(--night-txt)">Every engagement follows a repeatable framework — adapted to your institution, your programs, and your market.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="process-grid">
      <div class="pstep">
        <div class="ps-num">01</div>
        <div class="ps-icon" style="background:rgba(238,106,76,.15);color:#EE6A4C"><i class="ti ti-search"></i></div>
        <h3>Discover</h3>
        <p>We audit your current position — program strength, market demand, competitive landscape, existing visibility across AI, search, and press. We surface the enrollment gaps and the opportunities.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="pstep">
        <div class="ps-num">02</div>
        <div class="ps-icon" style="background:rgba(239,162,60,.15);color:#EFA23C"><i class="ti ti-map-2"></i></div>
        <h3>Strategize</h3>
        <p>We build a comprehensive marketing plan — program positioning, channel mix, creative direction, lead generation targets, earned media angles, rankings strategy. Every plan ties back to enrollment goals.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="pstep">
        <div class="ps-num">03</div>
        <div class="ps-icon" style="background:rgba(90,87,200,.15);color:#5A57C8"><i class="ti ti-rocket"></i></div>
        <h3>Execute</h3>
        <p>We launch and manage the full program — campaign creative, lead gen across owned and third-party networks, journalist outreach, ranking submissions, content publishing. Your team gets a single dashboard.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="pstep">
        <div class="ps-num">04</div>
        <div class="ps-icon" style="background:rgba(206,82,134,.15);color:#CE5286"><i class="ti ti-trending-up"></i></div>
        <h3>Optimize &amp; Compound</h3>
        <p>We measure everything — cost-per-lead, funnel velocity, AI citation share, press placement rate, ranking movement. Every cycle feeds the next. Visibility compounds instead of resetting.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- WHY STUDIO -->
<section class="band wrap">
  <div class="sec-head">
    <div class="sec-eyebrow">Why Studio</div>
    <h2>The agency advantage, <em class="grad">rebuilt</em>.</h2>
    <p>701am Studio isn't a traditional agency. It's the next generation — purpose-built for the channels and competition that define enrollment today.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="diffs">
    <div class="diff">
      <div class="diff-icon" style="background:var(--coral-soft);color:var(--coral-deep)"><i class="ti ti-building-bank"></i></div>
      <div>
        <h3>Two decades in education</h3>
        <p>We've spent 20 years building and operating education visibility. We know how rankings form, what journalists cover, how AI reads — because we lived it before we automated it.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="diff">
      <div class="diff-icon" style="background:var(--amber-soft);color:var(--amber-deep)"><i class="ti ti-affiliate"></i></div>
      <div>
        <h3>Owned + third-party lead gen network</h3>
        <p>We don't just buy ads. Our in-house network of education properties delivers high-intent student traffic, and our managed third-party marketplace scales it — all tied to your programs.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="diff">
      <div class="diff-icon" style="background:var(--indigo-soft);color:var(--indigo-deep)"><i class="ti ti-robot"></i></div>
      <div>
        <h3>AI-native, not AI-washed</h3>
        <p>Built from the ground up for an era where AI reads coverage alongside humans. Every placement, ranking, and data story is optimized to be cited by ChatGPT, Perplexity, and Gemini.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="diff">
      <div class="diff-icon" style="background:var(--green-soft);color:var(--green-deep)"><i class="ti ti-arrows-up-right"></i></div>
      <div>
        <h3>Compounding, not campaign-based</h3>
        <p>A placement this season feeds the AI answer next season. A ranking earned once keeps paying out. Your visibility builds instead of resetting every campaign cycle.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="diff">
      <div class="diff-icon" style="background:var(--slate-soft);color:var(--slate-blue)"><i class="ti ti-chart-scatter"></i></div>
      <div>
        <h3>Funnel-correlated, not vanity metrics</h3>
        <p>Every service ties back to enrollment — not impressions or ad clicks. We correlate visibility to inquiry, application, and enrollment movement through your CRM.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="diff">
      <div class="diff-icon" style="background:var(--rose-soft);color:var(--rose)"><i class="ti ti-shield-check"></i></div>
      <div>
        <h3>Editorial independence</h3>
        <p>Our rankings and data are independently maintained — never for sale. That independence is what makes the earned media and rankings work credible. We protect it operationally and contractually.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- WHO IT'S FOR -->
<section class="band wrap">
  <div class="sec-head">
    <div class="sec-eyebrow">Who it's for</div>
    <h2>Built for teams that need <em class="grad">more than software</em>.</h2>
    <p>701am Studio is for institutions and agencies that want the full engine — configured, managed, and staffed.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="forind" style="grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr)">
    <a class="ficard" href="/universities">
      <div class="fi" style="background:var(--gold-soft);color:var(--gold-deep)"><i class="ti ti-school"></i></div>
      <h3>Universities</h3>
      <p>Your enrollment team knows the programs. We run the full marketing engine — strategy, creative, lead gen, earned media, rankings, and AI visibility — tied to funnel movement, not just impressions.</p>
      <span class="more">For enrollment teams <i class="ti ti-arrow-right"></i></span>
    </a>
    <a class="ficard" href="/edtech">
      <div class="fi" style="background:var(--indigo-soft);color:var(--indigo-deep)"><i class="ti ti-device-laptop"></i></div>
      <h3>Edtech &amp; OPMs</h3>
      <p>Your category authority is a competitive advantage. Studio builds the data studies, trade coverage, and AI citations that make you the default choice when institutions evaluate your category.</p>
      <span class="more">For edtech companies <i class="ti ti-arrow-right"></i></span>
    </a>
    <a class="ficard" href="/agencies">
      <div class="fi" style="background:var(--coral-soft);color:var(--coral-deep)"><i class="ti ti-briefcase"></i></div>
      <h3>Agencies</h3>
      <p>Add an earned-media and enrollment marketing arm to your agency overnight. Studio runs per-client, isolated, and white-label — you keep the strategy and relationship, we deliver the results.</p>
      <span class="more">For agencies <i class="ti ti-arrow-right"></i></span>
    </a>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- TRAINING & WEBINARS -->
<section class="band wrap" id="training">
  <div class="sec-head">
    <div class="sec-eyebrow">Training &amp; Webinars</div>
    <h2>Learn the platform, master the <em class="grad">craft.</em></h2>
    <p>Get your team up to speed with guided onboarding, live sessions, and direct access to the Studio team.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="training-grid">
    <div class="tcard">
      <div class="tcard-icon" style="background:var(--coral-soft);color:var(--coral-deep)"><i class="ti ti-rocket"></i></div>
      <h3>Onboarding Program</h3>
      <p>Guided setup and configuration for your workspace — connect your CRM, define your programs, set campaign goals, and get your first visibility baseline within a week.</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Dedicated onboarding specialist</li>
        <li>Workspace configuration &amp; data connection</li>
        <li>First campaign launched together</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="tcard">
      <div class="tcard-icon" style="background:var(--amber-soft);color:var(--amber-deep)"><i class="ti ti-presentation"></i></div>
      <h3>Live Webinars</h3>
      <p>Weekly live sessions on enrollment marketing strategy, lead generation tactics, earned media, and platform deep-dives. Recorded and available on demand if you can't attend live.</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Enrollment marketing &amp; campaign strategy</li>
        <li>Platform feature walkthroughs &amp; updates</li>
        <li>Q&amp;A with the Studio team</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="tcard">
      <div class="tcard-icon" style="background:var(--indigo-soft);color:var(--indigo-deep)"><i class="ti ti-book"></i></div>
      <h3>Documentation &amp; Guides</h3>
      <p>Comprehensive docs, playbooks, and best-practice guides covering everything from first setup to advanced campaign orchestration.</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Platform documentation &amp; API references</li>
        <li>Enrollment marketing playbooks</li>
        <li>Campaign strategy templates</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="tcard">
      <div class="tcard-icon" style="background:var(--green-soft);color:var(--green-deep)"><i class="ti ti-users"></i></div>
      <h3>Office Hours</h3>
      <p>Direct access to the Studio team for personalized Q&amp;A, campaign strategy reviews, and help troubleshooting your enrollment and visibility goals.</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Weekly slots — first come, first served</li>
        <li>Campaign strategy &amp; performance reviews</li>
        <li>Custom integration or workflow support</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- CLOSING -->
<section class="closing">
  <div class="catmos"><div class="cg"></div></div>
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="pill-badge"><span class="tagm">Filed at sunrise</span></div>
    <h2>Let's build your enrollment <em class="grad">engine</em>.</h2>
    <p>Tell us about your institution — we'll scope a Studio engagement that matches your goals and your market.</p>
    <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg"><i class="ti ti-sparkles"></i>Inquire about Studio</a>
  </div>
</section>
</Layout>
